ActFair and Efficient Criminal Trials Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Dates of Coming into Force of Certain Sections of the Act
PrecisOrder fixing the COMING INTO FORCE dates of certain sections and subsections of the FAIR AND EFFICIENT CRIMINAL TRIALS ACT (MEGA-TRIALS), chapter 16 of the Statutes of Canada, 2011 as follows: (a) August 15, 2011 for sections 1 to 6, subsections 7(2) and (4) and sections 10, 11 and 14 to 16; and (b) October 24, 2011 for subsections 7(1) and (3) and sections 8, 9, 12 and 13.
